  1: # Timeline Visual Components Library
  2: 
  3: Reusable UI components and patterns for the timeline interface.
  4: 
  5: ## Component Catalog
  6: 
  7: ### 1. Session Marker
  8: 
  9: **Purpose**: Interactive point on timeline that indicates session status
 10: 
 11: **Variants**:
 12: ```html
 13: <!-- Success (< 10 errors) -->
 14: <div class="timeline-marker success"></div>
 15: 
 16: <!-- Warning (10-100 errors) -->
 17: <div class="timeline-marker warning"></div>
 18: 
 19: <!-- Error (> 100 errors) -->
 20: <div class="timeline-marker error"></div>
 21: ```
 22: 
 23: **Visual Specs**:
 24: - Size: 20px × 20px (resting), 28px × 28px (hover)
 25: - Border: 4px solid background color
 26: - Position: Centered on timeline spine
 27: - Cursor: pointer
 28: - Animation: Pulse on hover
 29: 
 30: **CSS**:
 31: ```css
 32: .timeline-marker {
 33:     width: 20px;
 34:     height: 20px;
 35:     background: var(--primary);
 36:     border: 4px solid var(--dark-surface);
 37:     border-radius: 50%;
 38:     cursor: pointer;
 39:     transition: all 0.3s;
 40: }
 41: 
 42: .timeline-marker:hover {
 43:     width: 28px;
 44:     height: 28px;
 45:     box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--glow-primary);
 46:     animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
 47: }
 48: ```
 49: 
 50: ---
 51: 
 52: ### 2. Metric Card
 53: 
 54: **Purpose**: Display a single key performance indicator
 55: 
 56: **Structure**:
 57: ```html
 58: <div class="metric">
 59:     <div class="metric-label">Total Files</div>
 60:     <div class="metric-value">1,234</div>
 61:     <div class="progress-bar">
 62:         <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 85%"></div>
 63:     </div>
 64: </div>
 65: ```
 66: 
 67: **Variants**:
 68: - Default (primary color)
 69: - Success (green)
 70: - Warning (orange)
 71: - Danger (red)
 72: 
 73: **Visual Specs**:
 74: - Background: Dark card
 75: - Padding: 0.75rem
 76: - Border: 1px solid dark border
 77: - Border radius: 0.5rem
 78: 
 79: **Usage Examples**:
 80: ```html
 81: <!-- Success metric -->
 82: <div class="metric">
 83:     <div class="metric-label">Organized</div>
 84:     <div class="metric-value success">980</div>
 85: </div>
 86: 
 87: <!-- Error metric (conditional red) -->
 88: <div class="metric">
 89:     <div class="metric-label">Errors</div>
