506: **Visual Specs**:
507: - Container: Dark card background, 0.25rem padding
508: - Buttons: Transparent background, 0.5rem padding
509: - Active: Primary background with glow
510: - Border radius: 0.5rem (container), 0.4rem (buttons)
511: 
512: ---
513: 
514: ### 14. Zoom Controls
515: 
516: **Purpose**: Adjust timeline scale
517: 
518: **Structure**:
519: ```html
520: <div class="zoom-controls">
521:     <button class="zoom-btn" onclick="adjustZoom(-1)">−</button>
522:     <span class="zoom-level">100%</span>
523:     <button class="zoom-btn" onclick="adjustZoom(1)">+</button>
524: </div>
525: ```
526: 
527: **Visual Specs**:
528: - Button size: 36px × 36px
529: - Font size: 1.2rem
530: - Border: 1px solid dark border
531: - Border radius: 0.5rem
532: 
533: **Interaction**:
534: ```javascript
535: let zoomLevel = 100;
536: 
537: function adjustZoom(direction) {
538:     zoomLevel += direction * 10;
539:     zoomLevel = Math.max(50, Math.min(200, zoomLevel));
540: 
541:     document.getElementById('zoomLevel').textContent = zoomLevel + '%';
542:     document.getElementById('timelineItems').style.transform =
543:         `scale(${zoomLevel / 100})`;
544: }
545: ```
546: 
547: ---
548: 
549: ## Composition Patterns
550: 
551: ### Pattern 1: Metrics Grid
552: 
553: **Use Case**: Display 2-4 related metrics
554: 
555: ```html
556: <div class="metrics-grid">
557:     <div class="metric">
558:         <div class="metric-label">Total Files</div>
559:         <div class="metric-value">1,234</div>
560:     </div>
561:     <div class="metric">
562:         <div class="metric-label">Organized</div>
563:         <div class="metric-value success">1,200</div>
564:     </div>
565:     <div class="metric">
566:         <div class="metric-label">Errors</div>
567:         <div class="metric-value">5</div>
568:     </div>
569:     <div class="metric">
570:         <div class="metric-label">Cost</div>
571:         <div class="metric-value">$2.45</div>
572:     </div>
573: </div>
574: ```
575: 
576: **Grid Behavior**:
577: - Desktop: 4 columns
578: - Tablet: 2 columns
579: - Mobile: 1 column
580: 
581: ---
582: 
583: ### Pattern 2: Comparison Layout
584: 
585: **Use Case**: Side-by-side session comparison
586: 
587: ```html
588: <div class="comparison-container">
589:     <!-- Left session -->
590:     <div class="comparison-card">
591:         <h3>Previous Run</h3>
592:         <div class="metrics-grid">
593:             <!-- Metrics -->
594:         </div>
595:     </div>
596: 
597:     <!-- Arrow -->
598:     <div class="comparison-arrow">
599:         →
600:         <span>vs</span>
601:     </div>
602: 
603:     <!-- Right session -->
604:     <div class="comparison-card">
605:         <h3>Latest Run</h3>
606:         <div class="metrics-grid">
607:             <!-- Metrics with diff indicators -->
608:         </div>
609:     </div>
610: </div>
611: ```
612: 
613: ---
614: 
615: ### Pattern 3: Timeline Item
616: 
617: **Use Case**: Single session on timeline
618: 
619: ```html
620: <div class="timeline-item">
621:     <div class="timeline-marker success"></div>
622:     <div class="timeline-content">
623:         <!-- Session content -->
624:     </div>
625: </div>
626: ```
627: 
628: **Layout Behavior**:
629: - Odd items: Content on right, arrow points left
630: - Even items: Content on left, arrow points right
631: - Mobile: All content on right, arrows point left
632: 
