 79: ### Border Radius
 80: 
 81: ```
 82: Small:   0.5rem  (8px)  - Buttons, metrics
 83: Medium:  0.75rem (12px) - Cards, inputs
 84: Large:   1rem    (16px) - Panels
 85: XLarge:  1.5rem  (24px) - Modals
 86: Pill:    9999px         - Badges, tags
