328: 5. Customize colors/branding if needed
329: 6. Set up auto-refresh after runs
330: 
331: ## Support
332: 
333: If you encounter issues:
334: 
335: 1. Check browser console for JavaScript errors
336: 2. Verify JSON structure with `jq`:
337:    ```bash
338:    jq . _site/timeline_data.json
339:    ```
340: 3. Test API directly:
341:    ```bash
342:    python3 src/api/timeline_api.py --stats
343:    ```
344: 4. Check database integrity:
345:    ```bash
346:    sqlite3 results/file_organization.db ".schema organization_sessions"
347:    ```
